Sorcery! Privacy Policy
The Sorcery! app uses external storage permissions on your device to save your progress from one Part to the next.
The save game data we transfer to our servers is entirely anonymous. It contains no identifying data whatsoever, other than the six-letter code displayed in game. No data is ever shared, sold, transferred, or used for any purpose other than the continuation of your Sorcery! adventure.
